OL,3,CGrass fire near Arthur's Seat sends
OL,4,Cplume of smoke over Edinburgh
OL,6,FA large grass fire has broken out in
OL,7,FHolyrood Park near Arthur's Seat in
OL,8,FEdinburgh.
OL,10,FThe fire started in an area of
OL,11,Fvegetation near the ruins of St
OL,12,FAnthony's Chapel on Monday evening,
OL,13,Fsending a plume of smoke over the city.
OL,15,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service
OL,16,F(SFRS) confirmed they were called the
OL,17,Fscene at around 6.50pm.
OL,19,FThey urged people to avoid the area
OL,20,Fand for local residents to keep their
OL,21,Fwindows and doors shut as a precaution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
