OL,3,CGrass fire near Arthur's Seat sends
OL,4,Cplume of smoke over Edinburgh
OL,6,FThe SFRS said three appliances were
OL,7,Fsent to tackle the blaze. Firefighters
OL,8,Fremain at the scene as of 9pm.
OL,10,FThe fire comes as the city feels the
OL,11,Fheat during the current sunny spell,
OL,12,Fwith a maximum temperature of 25C
OL,13,Frecorded by the Met Office.
OL,15,FDuring the Edinburgh Marathon at the
OL,16,Fweekend, a number of runners were
OL,17,Ftreated for heat exhaustion.
OL,19,FThe Scottish Ambulance Service said 16
OL,20,Fpeople were taken to hospital on
OL,21,FSunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
